              href="mailto:reservations@flatmountainestates.com?subject=Booking Inquiry for The Bodhi&body=Hello,%0A%0AI would like to inquire about booking The Bodhi for the following dates:%0A%0ACheck-in Date: %0ACheck-out Date: %0ANumber of Guests: %0A%0APlease send me availability and total cost information.%0A%0AThank you!"
